{
  "stem": "12666.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he saw that if a man was running towards the barbed wire to commit suicide, the young SS men would shoot them in the stomach.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that is a most painful wound.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would let them lie on the ground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody was allowed to touch him or to help him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he would bleed to death, and pain is terrific.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And his cries, according to the German theory, was that he would discourage others to commit suicide, that they would meekly go into the gas chamber to be killed.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, the job-- but we did cooperate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If we needed some information that some other trial had, we always did give-- would visit the lawyer and get the necessary information to, to explain.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because there is always a background to the documents that you have, and you have to find the-- so all these trials were going at the same time, I guess the lawyers against the doctors.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we would cooperate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sometimes, we would work on one trial or the other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we did have a job to work on our trial.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That was our main job, naturally.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had very nice rooms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we did have the necessary equipment to work with.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the conditions were-- the only thing is that, naturally, you had to go through security to get into the courthouse.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the beginning, we were afraid that the Germans might stage an effort to free the criminals.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so in the beginning, we did have even tanks protecting the entrance to the courthouse.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to have special passes that would be checked, and there was a photograph on the pass so that they would see that you are-- [LAUGHS] --who you are.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was strict security, definitely.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
